<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 23:00:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“平行宇宙”：公关专家詹姆斯·海莫维茨为未来中美关系找到远离政治的希望</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258838/parallel-universes-pr-expert-james-heimowitz-finds-hope-future-us-china-relations-away-politics?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>资深中国观察家表示，恢复民间交流是美中关系更加稳定的关键。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 22:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258838/parallel-universes-pr-expert-james-heimowitz-finds-hope-future-us-china-relations-away-politics?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争：中国取得“公共关系优势”，美国对以色列的支持遭到强烈反对</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258859/gaza-war-backlash-over-us-support-israel-china-makes-public-relations-gain?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>北京加大了亲巴勒斯坦的立场，而华盛顿则因其武装以色列的政策而面临压力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 15:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258859/gaza-war-backlash-over-us-support-israel-china-makes-public-relations-gain?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨开始访华，欧洲对不公平竞争的担忧日益加剧</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258977/german-chancellor-olaf-scholz-begins-china-visit-amid-mounting-european-concerns-over-unfair?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>肖尔茨希望加强贸易关系，但这次访问是在布鲁塞尔开始对中国电动汽车制造商进行补贴调查之际进行的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 13:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258977/german-chancellor-olaf-scholz-begins-china-visit-amid-mounting-european-concerns-over-unfair?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>为了在